subject: Thank you for your interest in Pathrise Recruiting Partners
text:
[('text/plain', 'quoted-printable', 'Hi Yukun,

We appreciate your interest in our roles. However, we do not currently have=
 any roles available for which you are a fit. We will keep your profile on =
file and consider you for any similar roles that open up in the future.

With that being said, we did want to take a moment to let you know about =
our career mentorship program. Our program provides technical & behavioral =
interview prep, networking opportunities, and 1-on-1 guidance and support =
through every step of your job search.

If you are interested, you can use the following link to read more about =
our program and apply: pathrise.com/questionnaire.

We also have a variety of resources to help with your job search available =
on our blog: pathrise.com/guides.

Best,
Pathrise Recruiting Partners

subject: Thank you for your interest in Masimo Corporation
text:
[('NA', 'NA', 'Dear Yukun Yang,

Thank you for submitting your resume to Masimo Corporation for consideration.  Your resume was reviewed for AI/Machine Learning Engineer.

We are fortunate to have many qualified candidates apply to each of our positions. We have evaluated the qualifications of each candidate and after careful consideration, we have determined that the credentials of other candidates may better fit our needs at this time.

Please continue to review our open positions on masimo.com/careers for other opportunities that may be a good fit.  We send our best wishes and thank you for your interest in Masimo Corporation.  

Sincerely,
Masimo Recruiting')]

Human Resources

found=C2=A0your=C2=A0way to us! However, at this time, we've decided to =
move forward with other candidates.

There are still many ways to be involved. Signing petitions, starting =
petitions, even volunteering for certain campaigns - these are great ways =
to help with creating change in the world around us.

Thank you again for=C2=A0your=C2=A0interest=C2=A0in Change.org and we wish =

text:

We appreciate your interest in GoHealth, and our Data Science Analyst role, for which you applied. After reviewing your application and resume in detail, we have decided to move forward with other candidates who are more closely aligned to our needs for this specific role.
